Subject: drm/amd/display: display connected to dp-1 does not light up
Git-commit: 1e1dbd6fd10031bf46d9e44b6ad423e2ee39e2a7
Patch-mainline: v4.19-rc1
References: FATE#326289 FATE#326079 FATE#326049 FATE#322398 FATE#326166

[why]
for vega, dp set_panel_mode is
handled by psp firmware. dal should not program the
register again.

[how]
dal does not program panel mode.

